Package: vdr-plugin-filebrowser
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${vdr:Depends}
Description: VDR plugin for file browsing and executing shell commands
 With this plugin it's possible to browse the file system in VDR's OSD.
 It's possible to define commands, that can be executed with the currently
 selected files. The commands will be executed asynchronously in background.
